title: Reachability
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

It is a [[Relation]], determining wether another state is reachable by a set [[Word]]

Defined Inductively:
Base:
$$x \overset{\epsilon}{\twoheadrightarrow} x$$

Inductive:
If $$x \overset{w}{\twoheadrightarrow} x'$$ and $$x' \overset{a}{\rightarrow} x''$$

Then $$x \overset{wa}{\twoheadrightarrow} x''$$